  "texts": [
    "Thus, x ∈ ⊠ i ↓-y ′.",
    "But since ⊥ ̸= y ′ ≤ y, we have y ̸ ≤ -y ′, so y ̸ ∈ ↓-y ′.",
    "Thus, we have a Z for which x ∈ ⊠ i Z but y ̸ ∈ Z.",
    "Hence A p is R-tight.",
    "Finally, since A p is a principal possibility frame, it is ⊑-tight by Fact 4.39.Next we show that A u is a full possibility frame that is tight."
